creator: AutoEnterprise
descriptionHtml:
Our team is confident that the independence of our country is in its energy freedom. In addition, we are proving with real examples of hundreds of our partners over and over again that saving the world is not only cool, but also profitable. We are developing networks of EV charging stations all around the world. The company offers three types of charging stations, one of which is fast charging (CHAdeMO). And now we are thinking about how to simplify the process of EV charging as much as possible? The answer is pretty simple: using ElectroUA mobile app.

ElectroUA app is a brand new product of Electro Ukraine company.

You can check this out for yourself how ElectroUA mobile app will make your lifestyle with an Electric Vehicle easier thanks to the set of functions for EV driver. It’s much easier to plan your valuable time with it.

ElectroUA app is designed for EVs owners to make their stay on the roads as comfortable as possible. This app provides information on more than 2500 EV charging stations of Electro Ukraine both in Ukraine and around the world. ElectroUA charging stations are installed in such countries as Romania, Georgia, Israel, Turkey, the United Arab Emirates alongside Ukraine. The app gives you access to the map showing all charging stations of the network.

The main advantages of ElectroUA mobile app:

- Convenient and comfortable interface;
- Search on the map of the closest ElectroUA network EV charging station;
- Charging station online status;
- Contactless activation and deactivation of EV charging station;
- All the necessary statistics on charging stations is always within touch.
- 24/7 service

The app allows you to build up your plans and schedule your route so that should anything happens there was an opportunity to recharge your EV on time and continue your journey without interrupting your plans. A huge advantage is that you can find out information on any charging station online beforehand: whether an EV charging station is operational, free or busy, the number of free connectors to connect. It is very beneficial and useful for traveling and movement in general.

Start charging your EV with two simple touches. Control the process and get active information in real time. Keep track of your expenses. Cool, isn’t it?

There is a personal account provided for owners of Electro Ukraine charging stations, where such owners of charging stations can view, edit, add up-to-date information about their EV charging stations.

Using this app is very convenient for those who plan to make a long-distance trip. You can easily plan your route, knowing in advance where the charging stations are located. A convenient search on the map or in the list in combination with filters will help you quickly find the desired station as well as to check its status. In addition, the app map is also available offline (for this you have to download and install it on your smartphone).

The company's development team reminds you that the mobile app does not interact with third-party services and works directly with the network of ElectroUA charging stations. Moreover, the company's experts promise to add new functions that fully meet the needs and requirements of "green" transport drivers.

The Electro Ukraine EV charging stations network is permanently expanding. New EV charging stations are installed daily and previously installed are regularly upgraded.

Download our mobile app and follow the latest news! A lot of interesting things are waiting for you.
